  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Detailed view (video)</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Introduction to the full back-end search. \n*Note: Only in special cases do customer have access to this full back-end search interface</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>This interface provides access to all data in the different sources, and only upon special request is access to the search interface granted. With this search interface, it is possible to read all content across all indexed sources.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"127\" style=\"width: 44px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png?width=44&amp;height=127&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png\" width=\"44\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png?width=22&amp;height=64&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png 22w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png?width=44&amp;height=127&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png 44w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png?width=66&amp;height=191&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png 66w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png?width=88&amp;height=254&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png 88w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png?width=110&amp;height=318&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png 110w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png?width=132&amp;height=381&amp;name=image-png-Jan-25-2023-07-13-12-3451-PM.png 132w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 44px) 100vw, 44px\"></p>\n<p>In the following video there is an introduction to the detailed view = full search interface for all content.</p>\n<div class=\"hs-video-widget\" data-hsv-embed-id=\"fe18ad03-3638-4c1e-93d1-0e35f9f1a829\">\n  <div class=\"hs-video-container\" style=\"max-width: 688px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n    <div class=\"hs-video-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; height: 0; padding-bottom: 49.27%\">\n      <iframe data-hsv-src=\"https://play.hubspotvideo.com/v/4381120/id/99906441323\" referrerpolicy=\"origin\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups\" allow=\"autoplay; fullscreen;\" style=\"position: absolute !important; width: 100% !important; height: 100% !important; left: 0; top: 0; border: 0 none; pointer-events: initial\" title=\"HubSpot Video\" loading=\"lazy\" data-hsv-id=\"99906441323\" data-hsv-style=\"\" data-hsv-width=\"688\" data-hsv-height=\"339\" data-hsv-autoplay=\"false\" data-hsv-loop=\"false\" data-hsv-muted=\"false\" data-hsv-hidden-controls=\"false\" data-hsv-full-width=\"false\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
